Package CSTutor.Model.User

Handles the User and Password Reset token data.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Password
    Password is a hash of the password that the user entered when registering.
    RecoverPass
    RecoverPass is responsible for sending password reset email to users that have asked to reset their password.
    Register
    Register is responsible for validating registration information and creating and adding the user to the UserDB.
    TokenDB
    TokenDB holds all of the currently valid password reset tokens.
    User
    User holds the information for a registered user of CSTutor.
    UserDB
    UserDB holds all of the registered users for cstutor.
